Subject: Re: [VB] Interior sources

Wolfsburg west has covers that match the originals
pretty close. They are an easy do it yourself project.
My only suggestion would be to replace the drawstring
with a piece of wire. They even have the correct door
panels for that truck as well.

Sean
65 Westfalia

